reviewText: I enjoyed the dvd. The different locations and watching stars fishing with varying levels of fishing skills was fun. It keeps you interested and with two disks, it's a good value.

This is NOT a guy you would want to fish with. He may have changed over the years but "way back when" I watched this guy do very dangerous stuff, put many people in harms way, and stiff guides of tips etc.  Just not someone I would want to support in the fly fishing adventure community. I would pick another video is my point

Good product , fair price. shipped quickly
Good product , fair price. shipped quickly, thanks
nothing more to say but have a good day
happy spring to you.
